      "created": "2016-09-19T21:55:32.893+0000",
      "description": "There are many cases when a client uploads data to HDFS and then needs to subsequently clean it up, such as with the distributed cache.  It would be helpful if YARN would do that cleanup automatically on job completion.\n\nThe hook could be generic to an URI supported by {{FileSystem}}.",
