          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "body": "Agree with Daniel here, this is a much smaller change and solves many use-cases, as YARN today widely depends on distributed cache for app/service deployments and a simple option to clean it up would be handy. ",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=jianhe",
